    <p>Au­to­mated num­ber plate recog­ni­tion sys­tem</p>
    <p>De­tects ve­hi­cles of in­ter­est on the move, with­out of­fi­cers hav­ing to di­vert their at­ten­tion from other on­go­ing tasks.</p>
    <p>In-ve­hi­cle video record­ing sys­tem</p>
    <p>Pro­vides live stream­ing of high-res­o­lu­tion video footage to the Po­lice Op­er­a­tions Com­mand Cen­tre for mak­ing bet­ter sense of sur­round­ings and in­ci­dent man­age­ment.</p>
    <p>In­te­grated ve­hic­u­lar dash­board</p>
    <p>Pro­vides of­fi­cers seam­less use and con­trol of all the tech­no­log­i­cal func­tions in the car.</p>
    <p>Ra­dio-fre­quency iden­ti­fi­ca­tion tech­nol­ogy in the ve­hi­cle boot</p>
    <p>En­ables of­fi­cers to track equip­ment within the ve­hi­cle, stream­lin­ing work pro­cesses.</p>

